        	<p>Obolo Chwerty is a simple Unicode keyboard for typing the Obolo language. The CHWERTY layout includes <samp>ch</samp>, <samp>ọ</samp>, <sample>n̄<sample> and <samp>sh</samp>.</p> 
        		<h4>Function</h4>
        			<p>The Obolo Chwerty keyboard follows the English (QWERTY US) layout. You can type all of the special Obolo letters with a single keystroke using this keyboard. Here is how:</p>
